videos.description: Lamonte Turner steals the errant pass, then zips the other way for a transition layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Turner shows off on both ends) 2019/01/29

videos.headline: Turner shows off on both ends

videos.description: Admiral Schofield gets the ball in the post, then uses his left hand to score the basket and increase Tennessee's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Schofield works inside for lefty layup) 2019/01/29

videos.headline: Schofield works inside for lefty layup

videos.description: Jordan Bone makes the nice feed to Grant Williams, who draws some contact and is still able to lay it in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williams absorbs contact for the bucket) 2019/01/29

videos.headline: Williams absorbs contact for the bucket

videos.description: Admiral Schofield doesn't shy away from South Carolina's A.J. Lawson's contact, and Schofield scores the bucket plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Schofield gets and-1 shot to fall) 2019/01/29

videos.headline: Schofield gets and-1 shot to fall

videos.description: A.J. Lawson cuts through the Tennessee defense and gets the tough shot to go plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (South Carolina's Lawson flexes after and-1) 2019/01/29

videos.headline: South Carolina's Lawson flexes after and-1

videos.description: Admiral Schofield makes a nice backdoor pass to a cutting Lamonte Turner, who adjusts his shot to avoid being blocked and finishes off the glass.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Turner scores on acrobatic reverse layup) 2019/01/29

videos.headline: Turner scores on acrobatic reverse layup

videos.description: Grant Williams continues to come up large for the Volunteers as he tallies 23 points in Tennessee's 92-70 win against South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Williams’ big night sparks Tennessee) 2019/01/29 ESHEET SOTFULL
